loc: Kyoto City, Kyoto Prefecture (location very approximate, either low mountain or suburban region)
rmk:
On migration in low mountain in the suburb of Kyoto city.

at the start of songs are not well recorded.

blue-and-white flycatcher (Cyanoptila cyanomelana).
